i3 is a minimalist window manager, focusing on keyboard commands to manipulate windows. By default all windows are in full-screen in order to best maximize the use of the screen and have less fiddling with positioning.

== Installation ==

The basic package is i3 itself

{{USEflag|package=x11-wm/i3}}

it is also assumed that you install dmenu

{{USEflag|package=x11-misc/dmenu}}

and also i3status

